Code and supporting documents for Node MCU four relay board (Wifi Quad Relay Board ) 
You will find
Arduino Code for HTTP/MQTT selectable mode with android apk for Http (NodeMCU_four_relay_board Node_Mcu_Four_Relay_WiFiSwitch)
Arduino Code for basic TCPserver
Arduino Code for basic Mqtt Client
Android Apk and Android App raw tcp/ip source code 
Instructable
http://www.instructables.com/id/NodeMCU-ESP8266-Based-Switch-Board-with-Raw-TCPIP-/
Website
http://armtronix.net
